      "role": "user",
      "content": "i cant stop thinking about how much of a joke it all is. like we spend our whole lives struggling, working, feeling pain, just for the universe to eventually freeze and turn into nothing. in a billion years nothing we do even matters. why do we even bother trying to keep going when the end result is just total emptiness anyway?",
