      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that \"solace\" feels so fake. how can it have value if it's all just a temporary blip of suffering? it's like being forced to play a game you know is rigged and has no winner. if the universe doesn't care, then all this \"valuing the journey\" is just a way to distract ourselves from the fact that we're just biological accidents waiting to be erased. it feels more like a trap than a journey.",
